Please continue your vegan journey. 😃 I’m so happy for you, that you could improve your health and happiness. 🍀
Maybe you can try at least 2 more month. For food and health study’s you can check out www.nutritionfacts.org or the the book from Dr. Gregor “How not to diet”. There are also a lot of other great vegan/health documentaries on Netflix, like “What the Health”, Fork over knives...
If you wanna know more about the animal suffering part, you can watch “Earthlings”.
